@10 = ~Nightbringer: Mace +3
Owned by a Dragon Highlord, Verminaard, Nightbringer is a footman's mace and a powerful tool of evil. Created by the clerics of the Queen of Darkness, Nightbringer causes any victim struck by the mace to go blind.
Nightbringer may only be used by those of inherent evil.   
Good people who use the mace must save vs spells or be converted to evil. Paladins who pick up the mace are slain, and rangers who touch it must save vs death or be slain.

STATISTICS:

Special: 50% chance of slaying a paladin on succesful hit.
50% chance of level drain(save vs spells)
Target must save vs spells at -2 or be permenatly blinded
THAC0: +3
